1. Can you provide evidence from credible sources confirming that Nora Zehetner and Robert Baker made their last appearance as Dr. Reed Adamson and Dr. Charles Percy in the episode "Death and All His Friends" of Grey's Anatomy?
2. Is there reliable information available to confirm that the characters Dr. Reed Adamson and Dr. Charles Percy were killed in the shooting incident depicted in the episode?
3. Are there reputable sources or official statements verifying that the episode "Death and All His Friends" marked the final appearances of Nora Zehetner and Robert Baker as Dr. Reed Adamson and Dr. Charles Percy on the show?
